-- MOVES- Zurich Insurance names Patrick Cohen head of customer and distribution for GI
-- 
-- Thu Jul 17, 2014 06:34AM EDT
-- None



July 17 (Reuters) - Swiss insurance company Zurich Insurance Group Ltd said it had appointed Patrick Cohen as head of customer and distribution for its general insurance (GI) business.

Cohen, based in Zurich, Switzerland, will report to Mike Kerner, CEO, general insurance. In his new role, he will be responsible for driving sales and customer strategy for GI, including distribution channels and broker management. Cohen joined Zurich Insurance in May 2012 as head of customer office for GI. He became chief marketing officer for GI in January 2013.